# 🏛️ Lincoln Hostel — System Governance

> **PRIME DIRECTIVE**: This repository operates under a strict **Architectural Governance System**. All contributors (Human or AI) must adhere to the rules in [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md).

### 📖 Governance Stack

| File | Purpose | Tracking |
|------|---------|----------|
| [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) | **Universal System Prompt**. Canonical rules and Prime Directive. | Tracked |
| [KNOWN_ISSUES.md](KNOWN_ISSUES.md) | Registry of confirmed system gaps and security/financial risks. | Tracked |
| [SCHEMA.md](SCHEMA.md) | Living snapshot of the current database table state. | Tracked |
| [PROJECT_MEMORY.md](PROJECT_MEMORY.md) | **Institutional Memory**. Machine-readable logic/decision log. | Tracked |
| [SESSION_LOG.md](SESSION_LOG.md) | Ephemeral scratchpad for session-specific notes. | **Gitignored** |

### 🛑 The "Know or Halt" Protocol
If you encounter any ambiguity in system behavior, **STOP**. Read `AGENTS.md` Section 5. Do not guess.

